-------------------------------------------------------------
|0 |PX COORDINATOR           |        |1       |7           |
|1 |└─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR     |:EX10000|1       |7           |
|2 |  └─PX PARTITION ITERATOR|        |1       |7           |
|3 |    └─TABLE FULL SCAN    |t0      |1       |7           |
=============================================================
